{"tid":1238003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知堅定流 如果堅既，真係夾硬來","createTime":"2019-06-17T16:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T17:06:47.000Z","uid":263064,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"194d26f7d9b664bb46f4fc3157628456e3bcfac3","tid":1238003,"uid":263064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:21:48.000Z","msg":"收到咁既whatsapp，唔知堅定流。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>引用</blockquote>如果換左新智能身分證嘅<br />\n都請大家查下<br />\n因為最近爆左大鑊<br />\n入境處做漏野<br />\n換新智能身分證，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">市民揀左繼續做選民</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但入境處竟然無將資料傳去選民登記處</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有幾十萬人無啦啦無左選民資格</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nSend to yr fd <br />\n有冇被人取消了<br />\n我朋友啱啱check<br />\n突然變咗唔係選民<br />\n佢上年明明仲有去投票<br />\n大家得閒都可以順手check下double confirm<br />\n趁仲有時間<br />\n唔怕一萬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2F&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=6d0e2561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/</a><br />\n<br />\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;最新update同新身份証有關，腦腦幫手都加一加埋?<blockquote>引用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另外仲收到個婦協通告，都係唔知堅定流，<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0RgsxBF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0RgsxBF.png&h=2b21eeba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩連登仔幫手check check，萬分感激。"},{"pid":"e35622d44a69f2e5506a59c1a31409b9c1e1f69b","tid":1238003,"uid":14362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:25:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b32b045a4ba459b75f7393f7fe87369446ef2e0e","tid":1238003,"uid":116000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:25:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8dc31f47f4aad605fff2a41ec9d0313bffa09346","tid":1238003,"u